Subject: [PATCH v6 06/12] media: ov5640: Compute the clock rate at runtime
Date: Mon,  3 Dec 2018 09:44:21 +0100
Message-Id: <284e2b654a03e0817b6af8b68f18cbc183024a62.1543826654.git-series.maxime.ripard@bootlin.com>
In-Reply-To: <cover.b1632e0c1a10c3f9f674e00142a554fa79eac762.1543826654.git-series.maxime.ripard@bootlin.com>
